{"tid":2331410,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"畫家即將刑滿出獄 將於1月5日就7.1佔領立法會案申請保釋","createTime":"2020-12-18T18:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T09:01:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6d1aa65b9203ca4203438a92684f61cd9dce290c","tid":2331410,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T18:40:30.000Z","msg":"去年7.1佔領立法會案，藝人王宗堯等11人被控暴動，連同因進入立法會會議廳被票控的范姓被告，各人分六案昨再訊。辯方透露，大部份人包括王宗堯均不認罪，其餘人士則需索取法律意見。控方申請將所有案件合併，但法官認為被告爭議點或指控各有不同，部份案件或須分拆，將案件押後至明年3月26日處理分案事宜。<br />\n<br />\n各人涉及六宗案件，分別被控暴動、進入或逗留在會議廳範圍、刑事毀壞及非法集結等罪。<br />\n<br />\n畫家潘浩超正就非法集結及刑毀等案件服刑，他服刑完畢後，欲就本案申請保釋，法官將其保釋申請定於明年1月5日處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201219/2FR6GZGTO5CLNHQQ2GEBDP7QZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201219%2F2FR6GZGTO5CLNHQQ2GEBDP7QZ4%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBUYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=52d277e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201219%2F2FR6GZGTO5CLNHQQ2GEBDP7QZ4%2F&h=af05ae41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201219/2FR6GZGTO5CLNHQQ2GEBDP7QZ4/</a>"},{"pid":"8cccfadd6ea7d087dfae5def57a082864deb8b46","tid":2331410,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T18:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880d281a0fa3cca4b588c7d531a4ad80402f88b2","tid":2331410,"uid":167509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T18:48:41.000Z","msg":"又一條好漢，出黎壯大黃圈"},{"pid":"593653e2ce9c11cbf51c789c378523e7716ac688","tid":2331410,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T18:51:43.000Z